  ('social-worker-moex-01431', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-109-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '「行政」與「管理」是社會工作管理中經常被交互使用，Warham認為「行政」係由三種不同層 級的要素所構成，下列何者不是前述要素之一？', '["指導", "管理", "督導", "服務"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d2c9f9354fd0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e73d095d3707", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01432', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-109-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作是具專業性的服務系統，有關社會工作服務特性之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["服務是開放的系統", "服務對象參與服務過程", "服務的生產與消費同時滿足或進行", "衡量產出具體明確"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d2c9f9354fd0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e73d095d3707", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01433', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-109-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '面對高度不確定性的環境裡，當既有的策略窒礙難行時，管理者必須具備策略靈活度，下列何者 不是策略靈活度的能力內涵？', '["確認外在環境變化", "維持組織原有的價值與穩定性", "快速投入資源", "認清策略是否可行"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d2c9f9354fd0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e73d095d3707", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01434', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-109-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '組織必須竭力消除各種存在於組織內的邊界，或是存在組織與外在環境之間的邊界，以降低邊界 阻礙有效的溝通協調，係屬何種新型的組織結構設計？', '["團隊結構", "虛擬組織", "網狀組織", "T型組織"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d2c9f9354fd0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e73d095d3707", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01435', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-109-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '組織是管理的重要功能之一，「係指任務及職權關係的正式系統，用於控制、協調及激勵員工」 係為那項重要要素的內涵？', '["組織結構", "組織設計", "組織變革", "組織文化"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d2c9f9354fd0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e73d095d3707", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01436', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-109-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '組織分化是將組織內部的資源、決策權及任務進行分配與配置，「依成員的工作性質和負責範圍 所作的分工」係為組織分化中的那種面向？', '["水平分化", "垂直分化", "空間分化", "程序分化"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d2c9f9354fd0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e73d095d3707", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
